-- Commercial Promoting China to Air on CNN, BBC in September, Daily Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-29T23:32:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/commercial-promoting-china-to-air-on-cnn-bbc-in-september-daily-reports.html

          
          
             A television commercial funded by
the Chinese government to promote the nation’s international
image will be aired by Cable News Network Inc. and the British
Broadcasting Corp. in September, the China Daily reported today,
citing an official from the company producing the advertising.  
 The commercial, proposed and funded by the State Council
Information Office, will feature Chinese celebrities including
basketball player Yao Ming and Hong Kong billionaire Li Ka-
shing, according to the report. Shanghai Lowe & Partners will
produce the 30-second commercial and also a 15-minute film about
China, the newspaper reported, citing Wang Lijun, assistant to
the company’s president.  
          
          


  


        